data.text:
About me

I currently serves as PBIS District Coordinator and as a Vice Principal for the Orcutt Union School District. I have trained districts on tiers one and two within PBIS and serve as an authorized external reviewer. My professional interests include establishing and maintaining positive school climates, student engagement, and effective work environments
